set system host-name preference-add-subtract

set policy-options policy-statement PS1 term T1 from protocol bgp
set policy-options policy-statement PS1 term T1 then preference 100

set policy-options policy-statement PS2 term T1 from protocol bgp
set policy-options policy-statement PS2 term T1 then preference add 50

set policy-options policy-statement PS3 term T1 from protocol bgp
set policy-options policy-statement PS3 term T1 then preference subtract 30

set policy-options policy-statement PS4 term T1 from protocol bgp
set policy-options policy-statement PS4 term T1 then preference add 4294967200

set policy-options policy-statement PS5 term T1 from protocol bgp
set policy-options policy-statement PS5 term T1 then preference subtract 4294967200
